OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,FThe Southport Inquiry should not just
OL,7,Fbe a "box-ticking exercise" for their
OL,8,Fdaughter who "deserved so much more",
OL,9,Fthe parents of the youngest victim of
OL,10,Fthe attack have said.
OL,12,FBebe King was just six-years-old when
OL,13,Fshe was murdered while attending a
OL,14,FTaylor Swift-themed dance class on 29
OL,15,FJuly 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
