OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,FGiving evidence to the public inquiry
OL,7,Finto the events, Lauren King, 42, sat
OL,8,Falongside husband Ben King, 43,
OL,9,Ftearfully told the hearing: "Her name
OL,10,Fwas Bebe. She was just six years old.
OL,11,FAnd she deserved so much more. She
OL,12,Fdeserved to live."
OL,14,F"No statement, no report, no apology
OL,15,Fwill ever bring Bebe back," she added.
OL,17,F"But this inquiry cannot become
OL,18,Fanother box-ticking exercise. The
OL,19,Ftruth must be faced. Accountability
OL,20,Fmust be taken. And real change must be
OL,21,Fmade.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
