OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,F"Because this was preventable. It
OL,7,Fshould never have happened. And no
OL,8,Fother child, no other family, no other
OL,9,Fcommunity should ever endure what we
OL,10,Fnow live with every single day."
OL,12,FThe public inquiry at Liverpool Town
OL,13,FHall aims to examine Axel Rudakubana's
OL,14,Fdealings with relevant agencies before
OL,15,Fhe carried out his violent attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
