OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,FThree girls - Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,7,Fnine, Bebe, six, and Elsie Dot
OL,8,FStancombe, seven - were murdered in
OL,9,Fthe incident on 29 July 2024, with the
OL,10,Fattacker attempting to murder 10
OL,11,Fothers.
OL,13,F"This inquiry is questioning 22
OL,14,Fdifferent organisations. That fact
OL,15,Falone speaks volumes," she told the
OL,16,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
