OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,FShe continued: "Her life was stolen
OL,7,Fbecause systems failed her. And while
OL,8,Fnothing said in this inquiry will ever
OL,9,Fbring her back, it can ` and must `
OL,10,Fensure that her death is not in vain.
OL,12,F"We do not stand here today because we
OL,13,Fwant sympathy. We stand here because
OL,14,Fwe want change. We want those
OL,15,Fresponsible to face the truth of what
OL,16,Fwent wrong.
OL,18,F"We want every child to be safer
OL,19,Ftomorrow than Bebe was on that day."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
