OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,FPaying tribute to her daughter, Lauren
OL,7,Fsaid she often looked at Bebe and
OL,8,Fthought "I can't believe you're my
OL,9,Fdaughter".
OL,11,F"Bebe had a caring, sensitive heart,
OL,12,Fyet she was also sassy, confident, and
OL,13,Falways smiling," she added.
OL,15,F"If she didn't like something, you'd
OL,16,Fknow about it ` and I loved that about
OL,17,Fher.
OL,19,F"I loved the fire in her belly, the
OL,20,Fway she fought against anything
OL,21,Funjust, whether small or serious.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
