OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,FShe told the public inquiry: "On that
OL,7,Fday, being told over the phone by my
OL,8,Fhusband that a man had gone into the
OL,9,Fdance class with a knife and that they
OL,10,Fcouldn't find Bebe... the hours
OL,11,Fwalking around in the intense heat not
OL,12,Fknowing whether she was alive or
OL,13,Fnot... praying to God that she was.
OL,15,F"Then being told in public, on a
OL,16,Fstreet corner, that my child was dead.
OL,17,FThese are moments no form of therapy
OL,18,Fcan ever resolve.
OL,26,@nD@^OUwD@AOU
