OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,F"A part of me is gone. I am broken
OL,7,Fbeyond repair. The physical pain I
OL,8,Fhave endured since that day has been
OL,9,Fdebilitating. I am grieving not only
OL,10,Fthe loss of Bebe, but also the loss of
OL,11,Fwho I once was.
OL,13,F"I replay that day over and over,
OL,14,Fcountless times, every single day. I
OL,15,Fpicture him attacking my beautiful
OL,16,FBebe, imagine her fear, her pain.
OL,18,F"His eyes, his evil eyes, never leave
OL,19,Fmy mind.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
