OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,F"Panic shadows me everywhere. Behind
OL,7,Fthe mask, I carry an emptiness I
OL,8,Fcannot describe."
OL,10,FThe mum told the inquiry the impact of
OL,11,FBebe's death, alongside those of Elsie
OL,12,Fand Alice as well as those who were
OL,13,Finjured, was "staggering".
OL,15,FAs she continued her statement, often
OL,16,Fdabbing her eyes to wipe away tears,
OL,17,Fshe said: "There is a group of us in
OL,18,Fthe hundreds who have been changed
OL,19,Fforever - and when multiplied by every
OL,20,Fother victim from that day and their
OL,21,Floved ones, the impact is staggering.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
