OL,3,C'Her name was Bebe... she deserved to
OL,4,Clive': Bebe King's parents tell Inquiry
OL,6,F"This was not just the loss of one
OL,7,Flittle girl, or one family torn apart.
OL,8,FThis was the tearing of a whole
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,F"And yet all of it - every layer of
OL,12,Fgrief, trauma, and destruction - stems
OL,13,Fback to the same truth: this was
OL,14,Fpreventable.
OL,16,F"It happened because of failures that
OL,17,Fshould never have been allowed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
